    "text": [
        "Dear Sir/Madame,",
        "I am writing to you, for requesting change of my accommodation.",
        "Currently, I live in the room G-36 which is shared by another girl student.",
        "I am finding it extremely difficult to study in the room. It is because, I have been used to work or study in isolated environments from my childhood. I am more productive when I am working alone. On top of it, the student whom I share the room is loud and always gets her friends to the place. In addition, the student hangs her clothes around generating a damp smell and, disturbing the serenity.",
        "I request you to change my accommodation to a non-shareable room. It would greatly help me to study and excel in my academics.",
        "I hope you accept my request. Looking forward to hear from you.",
        "Yours faithfully,",
        "Sashank Alladi"
